S.FORM: I a miheca saka folad saka a romi'ad masofoc ci Baldwin Lonsdale , malamikomoday a tamdaw. O Sawara'an no kitakit no Vanuatu anini i ci Baldwin Lonsdale, patirengan a romi'ad i 2014 a miheca saka 9 folad saka 22 a romi'ad. kasofocan a loma' 出生家庭 lalamod 配偶 salikaka 兄弟姐妹 natayalan 事蹟 pitooran 宗教
